    "hypothesis": "定义‘微观熵’为 (Amplitude - abs(Body)) / Amplitude，衡量波动的混乱程度。在4h下行趋势中，如果1h反弹伴随着‘微观熵’的连续扩张，说明每一单位的波动中，无效往复运动的比例在增加。当熵值达到临界点且买压flux掉下中性，价格通常会结束这种无效震荡并顺应宏观趋势暴跌。",
    "code": "def sig(cs1h, cs4h=None):\n    if not cs1h or not cs4h or len(cs1h) < 10 or len(cs4h) < 6:\n        return None\n\n    if gradient(cs4h, 6) > -0.005: return None\n\n    def get_entropy(cs, i):\n        high, low = cs[-i][\"high\"], cs[-i][\"low\"]\n        open_p, close_p = cs[-i][\"open\"], cs[-i][\"close\"]\n        r = high - low\n        if r <= 0: return 0.5\n        return (r - abs(close_p - open_p)) / r\n\n    # 最近3根K线的熵值是否呈上升趋势（混乱度增加）\n    e1 = get_entropy(cs1h, 1)\n    e2 = get_entropy(cs1h, 2)\n    e3 = get_entropy(cs1h, 3)\n\n    if e1 > e2 > e3 and e1 > 0.6:\n        # 且1h梯度已转弱，买压衰竭\n        if gradient(cs1h, 3) > 0 and flux(cs1h, 2) < 0.47:\n            return \"SHORT\"\n    return None",
